title: Vehicle fog lamp

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a vehicle fog lamp, as shown and described in FIGS. 1-14.

description: FIG. 1 is a frontal perspective view of a right fog lamp attached to a vehicle, no part of the vehicle is claimed;
FIG. 2 is a perspective view of the right fog lamp;
FIG. 3 is a front elevation view of the right fog lamp;
FIG. 4 is a top view of the right fog lamp;
FIG. 5 is a right side view of the right fog lamp;
FIG. 6 is a bottom plan view of the right fog lamp;
FIG. 7 is a left side elevation view of the right fog lamp;
FIG. 8 is a frontal perspective view of an alternative embodiment of the fog lamp illustrated in FIGS. 1-7, showing a left fog lamp attached to a vehicle, no part of the vehicle is claimed;
FIG. 9 is a perspective view of the left fog lamp;
FIG. 10 is a front elevation view of the left fog lamp;
FIG. 11 is a top plan view side of the left fog lamp;
FIG. 12 is a left side view of the left fog lamp;
FIG. 13 is a bottom plan view of the left fog lamp; and,
FIG. 14 is a right side elevation view of the left fog lamp.
The phantom lines are not a part of the claimed invention.
The stippling indicates the curvature of the fog lamp.
